# IP4
# Title 
## Delicacies Pizza

#Description
### A Web-Application of Ordering Pizzas. The user is in a position to request any order. The orders should be of diverse flavors, toppings,
crust and different size. Additionally, the client can choose whether he or she need delivery of pizza to their location
at an additional fees.

#Author
###Evans Karanja Karuga

#Set-Up
###Git clone: https://github.com/karanja477/IP4.git
###Extract the file from the Project Folder and launch index.html
link to the live demo: https://karanja477.github.io/IP4/

